<div id="review_3697228893" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3697228893" />
    <a title="Margaret Fisher" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/126311360-margaret-fisher"><img alt="Margaret Fisher" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3697228893?book_show_action=true">Dec 15, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Margaret Fisher" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Margaret Fisher" href="/user/show/126311360-margaret-fisher">Margaret Fisher</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9781525576515" href="/book/show/55692332-making-amends">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3697228893" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8701171000984074568">A solid first novel by a budding writer - I&apos;m curious how Jenna&apos;s hinted adventures with continue to progress, especially as the author continues to hone their skills. Jenna is compelling, the supernatural elements are interesting, and I like that the romance elements focus on reconciliation over something more dramatized.</span>
  <span id="freeText8701171000984074568" style="display:none">A solid first novel by a budding writer - I'm curious how Jenna's hinted adventures with continue to progress, especially as the author continues to hone their skills. Jenna is compelling, the supernatural elements are interesting, and I like that the romance elements focus on reconciliation over something more dramatized.</span>
