<div id="review_3697239885" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3697239885" />
    <a title="Thompson J." class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/126311592-thompson-j"><img alt="Thompson J." src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3697239885?book_show_action=true">Dec 15, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Thompson J." class="user" itemprop="url" name="Thompson J." href="/user/show/126311592-thompson-j">Thompson J.</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9781525576515" href="/book/show/55692332-making-amends">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3697239885" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15304598387845445680">This book is definitely out of my demographic (25M), but I don&apos;t regret reading it at all. I think for the target audience this would be a solid hit. I hope the writer continues with the potential sequels that feel foreshadowed here. I would buy something like this for my Mom.</span>
  <span id="freeText15304598387845445680" style="display:none">This book is definitely out of my demographic (25M), but I don't regret reading it at all. I think for the target audience this would be a solid hit. I hope the writer continues with the potential sequels that feel foreshadowed here. I would buy something like this for my Mom.</span>
  <a data-text-id="15304598387845445680" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


